Where'd this brat come from?

282
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:51,240
Children just speak the truth.

283
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:52,920
Is this...

284
00:14:53,040 --> 00:14:54,720
the bloodline left by the Sun Saint Emperor?

285
00:14:55,800 --> 00:14:56,800
A fine sapling.

286
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,040
Let me instruct him for a few years,

287
00:14:59,400 --> 00:15:00,400
and he will surely—

288
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:02,280
Shake the world with his brilliance!

289
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:04,120
What do you mean by that?

290
00:15:04,680 --> 00:15:06,000
Looking like you stepped in dog shit.

291
00:15:08,040 --> 00:15:09,040
What are you doing?

292
00:15:13,800 --> 00:15:15,120
Sorry, Pervert Uncles...

293
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:16,360
I didn't mean to.

294
00:15:17,520 --> 00:15:19,080
Face thicker than that Ye fellow's!

295
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,440
Back to business.

296
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:21,520
Let's talk serious matters.

297
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,280
Since we are crossing the star field,

298
00:15:23,880 --> 00:15:24,880
do you two know...

299
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:26,640
where another Five-Colored Altar is?

300
00:15:29,160 --> 00:15:29,760
I heard...

301
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:31,920
The Eight Sceneries Palace has a teleportation array.

302
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:33,840
Once activated,

303
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:35,880
it can reach other Five-Colored Altars.

304
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:38,200
However...

305
00:15:38,400 --> 00:15:39,400
Yin Tiande

306
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:40,720
placed restrictions on it.

307
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:43,360
Outsiders...

308
00:15:43,800 --> 00:15:44,400
cannot access it.

309
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:44,880
Exactly.

310
00:15:45,480 --> 00:15:47,040
But that guy just vanished,

311
00:15:47,160 --> 00:15:48,160
no news whatsoever.

312
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:50,160
But he has two attendants.

313
00:15:50,280 --> 00:15:51,000
One of them...

314
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:52,440
was killed by you along with his brother.

315
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:55,080
The other handles herb procurement for alchemy.

316
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:56,320
Should be easy to find.

317
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:58,120
In that case...

318
00:15:59,280 --> 00:16:00,480
this Herb-Gathering Attendant

319
00:16:01,560 --> 00:16:03,240
is worth a visit.

320
00:16:08,760 --> 00:16:18,510
[Ye Fan has reached the 8th Stage of the Immortal Platform Third Heaven.]
[Next Realms: Saint → Saint King → Great Sage→ Quasi-Emperor → Great Emperor]

321
00:16:23,280 --> 00:16:24,280
